item.description: I have three tee times for 12 players beginning at noon this Saturday.  The course is $50 and $16 for cart.  I played it a few years back and really liked it.  Their practice area includes both mats and grass tees, putting area and a huge area for chipping and bunker shots.  They claim they have the best practice facilities around.  They're located in Salem, NH about 40 minutes from downtown Boston.
item.how_to_find_us: clubhouse 10 minutes before; driving range before that
